    <refpurpose>
	Dash open testing framework  - Light weight collection of testing functions to run various tests for rapid projects.
    </refpurpose>
</refnamediv>
<refsect1><title>dotfw modules</title>
    <para>
    <screen format="linespecific">
    /usr/bin/dotfw ............. core module
    /usr/bin/dotfw-network ..... network specific functions (enabled by DOTFW_NETWORK=1)
    /usr/bin/dotfw-process ..... proceses related functions (enabled by DOTFW_PROCESS=1)
     </screen>
    </para>
